contentSections.heading: Events Tailwind
contentSections.blurb: Music has a wonderful ability to inspire people. It forms a common connection and brings us together to enjoy performances by wonderful musicians.
contentSections.body: Bringing top musicians to our city, Events Tailwind is committed to creating opportunities for locals and visitors to experience the very best of the world's musicians.

contentSections.heading: How to Support Us
contentSections.blurb: Music has a wonderful ability to inspire people. It forms a common connection and brings us together to enjoy performances by wonderful musicians.
contentSections.body: Bringing top musicians to our city, Events Tailwind is committed to creating opportunities for locals and visitors to experience the very best of the world's musicians.
contentSections.blurb1: Become a subscriber and enjoy a special concert organised annually for just subscribers and donors. For only $10 (subscription fee) per person, you get that nice warm feeling of supporting us!
contentSections.blurb2: Make a donation to help us bring the best performers to our city. The generosity of donors enables us to present more expensive concerts, while keeping admission prices affordable. For donations of $5 or more you can claim a tax credit.

contentSections.heading: Get involved
contentSections.body: Encourage people to come and enjoy our concerts by telling your friends, neighbours, people you see socially, and new arrivals to our city about our concerts. Don't forget those who live on their own.

contentSections.heading: Our Sponsors
contentSections.body: We are delighted to acknowledge the assistance of our sponsors who assist in making a significant difference to the work of Events Tailwind. Our sponsors help ensure that our activities are able to flourish, and that the highest quality music is available to us here. If you would like to join our list of official sponsors and support live music, please get in touch.

contentSections.heading: Continuous support allows us to do what we do.
contentSections.body: By becoming a subscriber, you help us present memorable concerts. We are a not-for-profit charity which needs the support of passionate music lovers to ensure we continue to offer top quality concerts to our community. Each year a concert or other event is held exclusively for Subscribers and Donors as a thank you for their support.

data.title: Jazz Jams
data.body: Jazz Jams are for all our die-hard jazz fans wanting to experience the best jazz our city has to offer! We have local jazz duos and bands, some up-and-coming and some renowned, playing once a month. Check out our event page on Facebook to see our drinks and deals available that day.
data.description: Experience the best jazz our city has to offer with local jazz duos and bands, some up-and-coming and some renowned.
data.bookingInfo: Booking information to be advised closer to the date.
data.quote: The best jazz our city has to offer

data.title: Rockerfella
data.body: After 16 years since their last recording, Rockerfella have returned to the recording studio with a bang! Releasing their first single which entered the chart at #60 the first time ever an unheard of song has ever been voted into the chart let alone enter so high! Followed up with the much anticipated Volume 1 release in the four part series in March Rockerfella are hitting the road in support of the release of Volume 1 in the 4 part volumes series this September and October.
data.description: Rockerfella are back touring the country, kicking it all off in the Garden City.
